ith my wife and two daughters. (My son didn=E2=80=99t have enough PTO!!) To=
day=E2=80=99s activity was zip-lining through a rainforest, which sounds li=
ke the setup for a <b>Marchand </b>joke. Yes, there were shots of tequila a=
t the beginning=E2=80=A6 <i>and</i> at the end. There isn=E2=80=99t much f=
